# Audit archive (TOON)

## On every scan

1. `archiveScanReport()` after `runScan()`
2. Write `audits/history/<iso>/report.toon`, `findings.toon`, `delta.toon`
3. Update `audits/latest.toon` and `audits/index.toon`
4. Git commit: `chore(security): among-check audit <iso> (<n> findings)`

## TOON

- Use `@toon-format/toon` with strict decode
- Tabular `findings[N]{id,severity,category,location,title}:` for agent reads
- Redact secrets before write; never store bearer tokens

## Agents

Read `audits/latest.toon` first; use `delta.toon` for `new[]` / `resolved[]`.

See `docs/audit-archive.md` and `docs/architecture.md` §14.
